{
  "page": "Prince of Winterfell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the television episode, see <a href=\"/index.php/The_Prince_of_Winterfell_(TV)\" title=\"The Prince of Winterfell (TV)\">The Prince of Winterfell (TV)</a>. For the chapter in <i>A Dance with Dragons</i>, see <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37\">The Prince of Winterfell</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/51/Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg/350px-Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"237\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/51/Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg/525px-Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg 1.5x, /images/5/51/Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Franz_MiklisWinterfell.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Prince of Winterfell</b> is a title held by certain nobles in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>, the heir of his elder brother <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a>, is the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> in Winterfell while Robb, the <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, campaigns in the south amid the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> takes Bran and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a> prisoner with the <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">capture of Winterfell</a> and sits the throne within the castle's Great Hall.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> His sister <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha</a> later mocks him for his inability to properly hold Winterfell, calling him Prince of Fools.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Prior to the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Winterfell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle at Winterfell\">battle at Winterfell</a>, the outnumbered Theon tells Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a>'s army of <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> that all who swear fealty to his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a>, as their king and to Theon as Prince of Winterfell will be confirmed in their rights. However, Theon is captured by <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After noticing <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">other people</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Queenscrown\" title=\"Queenscrown\">Queenscrown</a>, Bran tells himself not to be afraid, as he was the Prince of Winterfell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg/350px-NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"212\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg/525px-NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg/700px-NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:NotanerArt_Metamorphosis.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a>, and \"Reek\", by NotanerArt ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Having been tortured by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> and the now-legitimized Ramsay, Theon emerges from the <a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">Dreadfort</a> as \"Reek\". While Theon had been arrogant and cocksure during his brief time as Prince of Winterfell, \"Reek\" is traumatized and ruined.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Theon travels under a peace banner to present Ramsay Bolton's terms of rendition during the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Siege of Moat Cailin\">siege of Moat Cailin</a>. Since Theon is the son of the late Balon Greyjoy, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_Rivers\" title=\"King of the Isles and the Rivers\">King of the Isles and the Rivers</a>, Ramsay instructs Theon to act as a prince when speaking with the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> garrison guarding the three towers. However, Ramsay reminds Theon that he is still truly \"Reek\" at heart.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Later in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Godswood of Winterfell\">godswood of Winterfell</a>, Theon is chosen to ceremoniously present \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\" (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>) in marriage to Ramsay, since Theon was the longtime ward of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a>, and it is believed that Arya's trueborn brothers are dead. Ramsay mocks Theon as Prince of Winterfell before his bedding with Jeyne,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> and a guard later mocks Theon as the Prince of Stink.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Cley</b>: Good morrow, Bran. Or must I call you Prince Bran now?<br />\n</p><p><b>Bran</b>: Only if you want.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Cley</b>: Why not? <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">Everyone else</a> is a king or prince these days.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Cley_Cerwyn\" title=\"Cley Cerwyn\">Cley Cerwyn</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I will be as good a lord to you as <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> ever was. Betray me, though, and you'll wish you hadn't.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> to the people of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I took <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">this castle</a> and I mean to hold it, to live or die as Prince of Winterfell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>There will be no <a href=\"/index.php/Flaying\" title=\"Flaying\">flaying</a> here whilst I am Prince of Winterfell, Theon had responded, little dreaming how short his rule would prove.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>His reign as prince of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> had been a brief one. He had played his part in the mummer's show, giving the <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">feigned Arya</a> to be wed, and now he was of no further use to <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prince_of_Winterfell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Theon V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Bran III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 4\">Chapter 4</a>, Bran I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1